# --- Migrating existing Keycloak users ---
# Existing users can re-register using their old Keycloak UUID as 'existingAuthId'
# POST /api/auth/register with body: { email, password, existingAuthId: "<old-keycloak-uuid>" }
# This links the new auth system to their existing activity data seamlessly.

